title: "Apple halting sales of Series 9
source_name: "Apple announced Monday that it will pause sales of its Apple Watch Series 9 and Ultra 2 smartwatches amid a patent infringement dispute with medical technology firm Masimo."

title: "Amazon in talks to invest in Diamond Sports - WSJ"
text: "Amazon is in talks to invest in regional-sports programmer Diamond Sports
source_name: a move that would advance the e-commerce giant's aggressive push into sports content
date: the Wall Street Journal reported on Monday
topics: citing people familiar with the matter."
